{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-dang-003__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-dang-003", "source_id": "daya-dang-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·蕩之什·003.1", "text_original": "菀彼桑柔，其下侯旬。捋采其劉，瘼此下民。\n不殄心憂，倉兄填兮。倬彼昊天，寧不我矜。", "text_normalized": "菀彼桑柔，其下侯旬。捋采其劉，瘼此下民。\n不殄心憂，倉兄填兮。倬彼昊天，寧不我矜。", "notes": "桑柔 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-dang-003__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-dang-003", "source_id": "daya-dang-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·蕩之什·003.2", "text_original": "四牡騤騤，旟旐有翩。亂生不夷，靡國不泯。\n民靡有黎，具禍以燼。於乎有哀，國步斯頻。", "text_normalized": "四牡騤騤，旟旐有翩。亂生不夷，靡國不泯。\n民靡有黎，具禍以燼。於乎有哀，國步斯頻。", "notes": "桑柔 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-dang-003__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-dang-003", "source_id": "daya-dang-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·蕩之什·003.3", "text_original": "國步蔑資，天不我將。靡所止疑，云徂何往？\n君子實維，秉心無競。誰生厲階？至今為梗。", "text_normalized": "國步蔑資，天不我將。靡所止疑，云徂何往？\n君子實維，秉心無競。誰生厲階？至今為梗。", "notes": "桑柔 Chinese stanza 3."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-dang-003__004__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-dang-003", "source_id": "daya-dang-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·蕩之什·003.4", "text_original": "憂心慇慇，念我土宇。我生不辰，逢天僤怒。\n自西徂東，靡所定處。多我覯痻，孔棘我圉。", "text_normalized": "憂心慇慇，念我土宇。我生不辰，逢天僤怒。\n自西徂東，靡所定處。多我覯痻，孔棘我圉。", "notes": "桑柔 Chinese stanza 4."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-dang-003__005__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-dang-003", "source_id": "daya-dang-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·蕩之什·003.5", "text_original": "天降喪亂，滅我立王。降此蟊賊，稼穡卒痒。\n哀恫中國，具贅卒荒。靡有旅力，以念穹蒼。", "text_normalized": "天降喪亂，滅我立王。降此蟊賊，稼穡卒痒。\n哀恫中國，具贅卒荒。靡有旅力，以念穹蒼。", "notes": "桑柔 Chinese stanza 5."}
